::Zardus::

"Excellent," Zardus replies, "I'm sending you the coordinates."

He taps a few buttons on his wrist comp to send Alliance Island's coordinates, then closes the channel, tapping his comm to send a message to Supernova.

"Supernova, can you interrupt your training to take your group outside the base. A bot will be flying in shortly, a mercenary. I need you to escort him to me."
